name: I have no Idea What I'm doing

metadata.name: I have no Idea What I'm doing 1/1299
metadata.description: "I Have No Idea What I'm Doing" is a catchphrase often used in image macro captions featuring photos of animals, typically canines, posed as if they are performing tasks associated with humans, in a similar vein to "Yes, This is Dog" and the Dog Fort comic series.
